{"tid":447910,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（越南）會安峴港住宿煩惱","createTime":"2017-10-25T17:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T15:28:03.000Z","uid":27574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fed8041af1061ee3db0f2fb1bf629951085c4f5f","tid":447910,"uid":27574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:31:39.000Z","msg":"11月尾同女友會去越南峴港會安，會住2晚會安同3晚峴港。因為第一次去，女友唔想住太貴，想問下大家關於住宿的問題<br />\n<br />\n1.峴港就想近海灘個邊，想問下d resort係性價比較高？ 如果住酒店，有無d$ 500-600/晚的酒店（有infinity pool更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n2.會安的酒店係咪離古城區有一段路程？"},{"pid":"33ff43a63bd61e3aff33d3cbf94c1f3dddff10fb","tid":447910,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T18:04:07.000Z","msg":"第一次去唔想住咁貴咁即係第二次去就會住貴啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇啲5 600嘅酒店 有實有㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十一月尾都唔算旺季<br />\n不過呢個價仲想要infinity pool又真係大貪咗啲<br />\n可以睇下a la carte<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297baef054f620c0baa175d407fde31b1ed67292","tid":447910,"uid":134182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T00:42:19.000Z","msg":"啱啱去完<br />\n <br />\n我就住mandila beach hotel danang <br />\n<br />\n揀左間靚少少既房<br />\n600蚊晚左右兩個人<br />\n有海景 同 infinity pool"},{"pid":"947d9ee002ebe31379994b7055a5898e96899086","tid":447910,"uid":27574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T15:26:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱去完<br />\n <br />\n我就住mandila beach hotel danang <br />\n<br />\n揀左間靚少少既房<br />\n600蚊晚左右兩個人<br />\n有海景 同 infinity pool</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n600蚊晚都幾抵wow.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3393593d2ac8ca6b3e8439d9ef0167c1ed6afcb6","tid":447910,"uid":27574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T15:28:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次去唔想住咁貴咁即係第二次去就會住貴啲？<img src=\"/asse